nodes.text: Typhojem, most commonly known as the Left-Handed God Typhojem, was a deity that was worshipped. Tryphon Leo sought to find the Shrove of the Left-Handed God Typhojem in the Outer Rim Territories. At some point, Reginald Danfillo of the League of XenoExplorers was part of the Typhojem Excavation.
